Cj101

I was a little confused by your first comment, where you said;
“The uninformed are taking over this once great country at record pace, and their leader is now poised to deliver a deathblow”

But you clarified what you meant in the second comment;
“…the uninformed ARE being marched down the voting street by the politician marionettists.”

You were talking about your fear of Donald Trump or Ted Cruz being elected president.
